item.title: Position
item.description:
Position can be broken into a bunch of knowledge areas

This is how you control the position you are in. Controls

This is how you transition from one position to another position This can be either through Sweep or Transition Technically Takedown also falls under this category, although we treat it as its own.

These can be described as a Joint Lock,Choke or Pain Compliance mechanism.
